Microhabitat: Pond edge in pine flatwoods. Colony floating on water surface. Entire floating m
CollectionNotes: NOTEBY J.Longino: Pond edge in pine flatwoods. Colony floating on water surface. Entire floating mass collected. Photos. I later estimated colony size by counting workers and weighing subsamples. Estimate 122500 workers, 430 alate queens and males. I sieved the colony, separating sexuals. I picked out the single dealate queen I found, assuming she is the colony queen. I also found two scarab inquilines. The colony is stored in a jar, sexuals separated in two large vials, queen and inquilines isolated in small vial.
